    "feat": {
        "name": "Improvise Tool",
        "type": "stat_block_section",
        "subtype": "feat",
        "text": "You can jury-rig solutions when you don't have the proper tools on hand. You can attempt to Repair damaged items without a repair toolkit.   \nIf you have the raw materials, you can Craft a basic caltrop set, candle, compass, crowbar, fishing tackle, flint and steel,hammer, ladder, piton, rope, 10-foot pole, replacement thieves' picks, long or short tool, or torch as if you had their formulas.",
        "level": 1,
        "traits": [
